name: Crep Protect Cure
decription: The Crep Protect Cleaning Kit is the ultimate when it comes to a shoe cleaning kit, and like everything we create, we did it with the sneakerhead in mind. We created our own cleaning solution, as well as creating our own brush that is suitable for any and all shoe materials. The Crep Protect Cleaning Kit is designed to clean deeply without affecting the look, feel, and shape of your shoe in any way. Made of 98% natural ingredients, including coconut extracts, water, and jojoba, and using short and soft brush bristles, the Crep Protect Cleaning Kit really takes care of your shoes the way you always have. The Crep Protect Cleaning Kit comes with a brush, the cleaning solution, and microfiber cloth, giving you a total cleaning solution for your kicks.
